'''Yusuff Kamal''' (b: 1938)<ref name="anisshakur.tripod.com"/> , better known as '''Shakeel''' is a versatile, respected and veteran Pakistani [[Pakistan Television Corporation|television]] actor who has been on the scene for almost 4 decades.<ref name="anisshakur.tripod.com"/> Amongst his most famous roles are the lead in [[Uncle Urfi]] and Mehboob Ahmed in [[Aangan Terha]]. He has also acted in a number of local [[Lollywood|films]] as well as one [[English film]], [[Butterflies are free]].<ref name="anisshakur.tripod.com"/> Besides his acting, he is also famous for his philanthropic activities.<ref name="anisshakur.tripod.com"/>
